## -------
## dotnet local tools — ship the manifest with the repo, even if a global
## gitignore excludes .config (the manifest pins Fantomas).
## -------
!.config/
.config/*
!.config/dotnet-tools.json

## -------
## Claude Code — ship the shared settings with the repo, even if a global
## gitignore excludes .claude. Personal overrides stay ignored.
## -------
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/settings.json.template
.claude/settings.local.json

## -------
## Agent-instruction files — local guidance for whoever works in a checkout, not
## project source. Kept untracked so they never reach the remote (each developer
## keeps their own). The `.claude/` rule here is intentionally AFTER the ship
## negations above so a later directory-exclude wins and the whole dir stays local.
## -------
/AGENTS.md
/CLAUDE.md
/CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/
